如何升级
========
从2014.1到2014.2:
    $ wget https://gitcafe.com/Deepin/deepin-os-upgrader/raw/release_forward_slash_2014.2.1/from2014.1to2014.2.sh && sudo bash ./from2014.1to2014.2.sh 

从2014.2RC到2014.2:
    $ wget https://gitcafe.com/Deepin/deepin-os-upgrader/raw/release_forward_slash_2014.2.1/from2014.2RCto2014.2.sh && sudo bash ./from2014.1to2014.2.sh 
